    "It contains a differentiable attack layer to simulate different distortions.",
    "This technique improves robustness against attacks and maximizes the trade-off between robustness and imperceptibility.",
    "Zhong et al. [99] proposes a CNN-based watermarking technique which is robust and blind and can be used for several applications.",
